    <chapter id="cloud-user-role-editor" title="Editor" level="2">
        <p>If you just joined an existing company, %product_cloud% will assign your account the <b>editor</b> role. </p>

        <p>Any editor can be promoted to the <a anchor="cloud-user-role-administrator">administrator</a> role, see the
            <a href="cloud-change-user-roles.xml">Change user roles</a> section.</p>

